{"tid":2186506,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"硬銷大龍鳳 林鄭引譚德塞舊論","createTime":"2020-09-03T04:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:32:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f94acb9e25a212574d01811d002b08f7e56e108","tid":2186506,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/JBCVBJK5WVHN3F53NFRKQCVMWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FJBCVBJK5WVHN3F53NFRKQCVMWE%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3he%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=314b62bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FJBCVBJK5WVHN3F53NFRKQCVMWE%2F&h=f3abcdbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/JBCVBJK5WVHN3F53NFRKQCVMWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n硬銷大龍鳳 林鄭引譚德塞舊論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pg3IAmS0t_Y14MvbYIphxCuTfrY=/1762x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5PHI5HOANDEBEKQ5ZZCGXJUFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPg3IAmS0t_Y14MvbYIphxCuTfrY%3D%2F1762x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5PHI5HOANDEBEKQ5ZZCGXJUFU.jpg&h=117db268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府落力宣傳全民檢測，獲美心集團創辦人長女伍淑清等響應，昨到會展的檢測中心採樣。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府全力催谷市民報名參與全民檢測驗毒，特首林鄭月娥前天出席行會會議前拋出六大論點，圖反駁外界反對及質疑全民檢測的理由，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宣稱世衞專家意見<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥為回應世衞專家近期指，大規模檢驗是浪費金錢、不切實際，援引另一世衞專家意見，稱「我記得有一次，世衞某位專家也是說『test、test、test』」，指世衞從來沒有排斥檢測的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n不過，林鄭未有交代該世衞專家身份，又未有提及在甚麼背景下提出要作檢測。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒回應時指，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒斥偷換概念<br />\n<br />\n郭又批評林鄭，如此不具名引述譚德塞意見是偷換概念，「當時講嘅測試係去確定懷疑個案有冇感染，係discovery test，當時根本仲未完全知個病毒有幾危險，所以個案先一定要做檢測，唔同現時做嘅mass test。」形容林鄭說法狡猾，「蝦你唔知，為將唔合理嘅合理化，不擇手段講啲好似真嘅假道理。」"},{"pid":"af9b539cdc112b9bdcd2141e8e09ec9d512d4c57","tid":2186506,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"個d 所謂專家"}]}